<html t:type="ui/dialogstructure" title="literal:My Discounts" xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd"
	xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">
	<p>Sometimes we are able to offer discounts on a selection of our classes. If you have a discount code, then please enter it into the box
		below</p>
	<t:zone t:id="addDiscountZone">
		<t:form t:id="addDiscountForm" zone="addDiscountZone">
			<label for="promo">Discount code:</label>
			<t:textField name="promo" value="promoCode"></t:textField>
			<t:submit value="add"></t:submit> ${errorMessage} </t:form>
		<t:if test="promotionsList.empty" negate="true">
			<p class="discount_options">You have entered the following codes.<br />
				<a href="/" onclick="window.parent.location.reload(true);return false;">Update page for these discounts now...</a>
			</p>
			<t:loop source="promotionsList" value="addedPromotion">
				<h5 class="popup-name">${addedPromotion.code}</h5>
				<div class="clear"></div>
				<p>
					<t:outputRaw value="addedPromotion.detail"></t:outputRaw>
				</p>
				<div class="divideline"></div>
			</t:loop>
			<p>The discounted prices will be now shown next to each course as you browse this site.</p>
		</t:if>
	</t:zone>
	<p class="note"><strong class="alert">Please note:</strong> Our discounts are usually only available until a certain date, so you may not
		be able to use an old discount code.</p>
</html>
